gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Timberwolves 112, 76ers 99
gameRecap.excerpt: The Timberwolves defeated the 76ers, 112-99. Anthony Edwards recorded 31 points, six rebounds, and six assists for the Timberwolves, while Karl-Anthony Towns added 23 and 11 rebounds in the victory. Tyrese Maxey tallied 16 points, eight assists, and five rebounds for the 76ers in the losing effort. The Timberwolves improve to 11-3 in the regular season, while the 76ers fall to 10-5.
